Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoundrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a problem, old guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have received\Na communication
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Land of Fire\Nabout the temporary curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we could be\Nof use somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be giving in\Nto you youngsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:53.80,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(743.438,560)}The Old Monk's Prayer\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the twenty platoons, we are currently laying\N out a search net with a radius of 150 kilometers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,around the border and\Nthe Temple of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an ant couldn't crawl out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have received a report\Nfrom Platoon Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of the Akatsuki\Nin border areas C and E.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Areas F and G are normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki still have not been found!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't they been found?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we heard from Team Asuma\Nwho went to the Temple of Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No report from them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiriku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You are from\Nthe Hidden Leaf Village, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We were contacted by the monk\Nwho is in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the head monk\Nof the Temple of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I had been out of\Nthe temple for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard about\Nwhat happened here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I rushed back as quickly\Nas I could, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a terrible sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We asked neighboring temples\Nfor help recovering the remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Chiriku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...we have been unable\Nto find Lord Chiriku's remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... Captain Asuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really want to bring this up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chiriku has a 30 million ryo\Nbounty on his head
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,on the black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If those guys from the Akatsuki\Nknow about the bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A collection office, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So that basically means the enemy\Nis carrying the body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumo, where is the collection office?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Including the closest one,\Nthere are five locations in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the nearby teams can rush right\Nto the other four exchange point locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment,\NLord Asuma Sarutobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to say a prayer\Nfor all of you who are about to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiriku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiriku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I'm the only member of\N{\i1}the Guardian Shinobi Twelve left, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to talk the night away\N{\i1}with you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were things I wanted {\i1}to talk to you\N about. {\i1}And things I wanted you to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least...\NI'll get back Chiriku's remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't push things too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a bounty on your head for being a former\N member of the Guardian Shinobi Twelve... just like Chiriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The bounty on my head is\Nfive million ryo more than Chiriku's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only thing to worry about\N{\i1}with Asuma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is that he smokes too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened\Nwith the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I went to the trouble\Nof making and bringing more food pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come to check\Non Naruto, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was just taking\Na walk to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get out of shape\Ndue to my injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's good to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Naruto's training...suspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably just went off\Nsomewhere to unwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His body and mind won't hold up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,if he continues tough\Nspecial training like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen... Ichiraku ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah-yeah, I know.\NWalk just a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.\NYou should have one of these, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this...? A mud ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude. This is one of\Nmy special homemade food pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's extra special!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Special...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's more like medicine\Nthan a food pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's filled with nutritious ingredients\Nmixed with fast-acting digestive agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all of which I hand-picked and rolled up\Ninto a ball packed with energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It works really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And it might even add some healthy color\N to that pale skin while it helps you recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They say good medicine tastes bitter,\N so the food pills might taste a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you consider its merits after consumption,\N little details like that will be of no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for the pill. - Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I feel dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell and taste are\Ngoing to make me sick
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,before the medicine can work...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tonkotsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man, I'll take an extra-large\Ntonkotsu miso with pork slices...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,on the double.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!\NWe have a new menu now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want...an extra-large\Ntonkotsu miso with pork slices...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and extra-firm noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look at the menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made some big changes\Nto the menu as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We now serve tsukemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll have an extra-large\Ntonkotsu miso with pork slices...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and extra red pickled ginger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, we don't serve\Nramen anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,SPECIAL\NICHIRAKU TSUKEMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means...\Nnow you specialize in tsukemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter Ayame went out for\Nnoodle-making training for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And when she came back she said,\N"Dad, the age of tsukemen is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We should explore\NIchiraku's new potential!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She gives me this smart-aleck advice,\Nyou see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The tastes and preferences of our\N customers change along with the times!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichiraku will change so as\Nnot to fall behind the times!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was looking forward to...\Ntonkotsu miso with pork slices.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukemen is pretty much\Nlike ramen anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As with soba noodles,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you dip tsukemen noodles\Nin sauce before eating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing in the end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The concept is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen is different from tsukemen!\NI want to eat ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only prepared tsukemen,\Nso ramen is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you tweak the soup a little you\N could switch it back to ramen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're satisfied with\Nphony ramen like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all your love for tonkotsu miso\Nwith pork slices amounts to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting all worked up...\Nmade me even hungrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...care anymore...\NJust give me some tsukemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Three orders of tsukemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Three orders of tsukemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The noodles are just\Na tad undercooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Boil them for one extra minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And check the temperature\Nof the hot water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right!\N-You're going to make them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!\NIchiraku tsukemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's the soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a little strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The tsukemen that was popular\Nin Yugao Village
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,was a little lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make the soup again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The first taste is the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We must lavish our customers\Nwith the perfect flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Ayame!\NShow me the results of your training!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!\NIchiraku's original tsukemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This time it's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Old man... Can I get some pork slices\Nand pickled bamboo shoots...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and some fish cake...toppings...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Naruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ramen if I eat it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's tsukemen!\NYou can't eat it like that--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayame... You're forgetting the most\Nimportant thing about a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of getting all caught up\Nin the little details,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more important for\Nthe customer to be satisfied, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I put my heart and soul\Ninto making this tsukemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a restaurant's responsibility to use\Nthe best ingredients and preparation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:15:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and to advise the customer on\Nhow to best enjoy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to eat ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Save it for after you've tried some\Nof the tsukemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never selfishly\Nask for ramen ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you.\N-Selfish? It's selfish for a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Tsukemen is lighter than ramen.\N-to make choices for the customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}This might be a little more to my taste.\N-Only serving tsukemen means
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we have absolute confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'm getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}My shoulders get really stiff\N-If you've got so much confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}when I do something I'm not used to.\N-then why does it take you so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Maybe I'll hire some energetic youngster\N-What's wrong with a little wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}to work here part time.\N-You'll be able to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,something more delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the day,\Nanything tastes good when you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the tsukemen-ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Considering he complained about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe he drank every last drop\N{\i1}of that strong tsukemen soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Although there's a problem\Nwith how he ate the tsukemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't complain\Nsince he had three bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get right back to training!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:16:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... I'll show you something cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some things\NI want to explain to you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,while we take a little rest after eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NMore complicated explanations?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay...\NI'm a slick talker, so you'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato, you take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Isn't it usually the senior\Nwho takes care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no seniors or juniors\Nin regards to the men I respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're pretty much\Nthe only junior...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I suppose I really should...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you very much!\N-Oh, keep the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a slick talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sick of how lousy\Nyou are at conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A nice trip is totally ruined
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,if you get stuck traveling with\Na totally boring person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not traveling for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've had it with looking\Nfor Jinchuriki
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,when we don't even know\Nwhere the heck they might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourself in my position.\N I'm forced to go along with all this extra work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a little sympathy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and keep walking...\NWe're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWe're late because we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to that Collection Office\Nor whatever it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you're making this boring trip\Neven longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really annoying...I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoying, you say?\NThis is also an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever.\NYou've been left in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of scraping together money\Nfor the organization, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A pittance like that would\Nonly be enough to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for an after-party\Nfor Tailed-Beast hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that body is heavy, isn't it?\NI could carry it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you going to do...\Nwith my valuable bounty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just being nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to discard it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get rid of this body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We should just forget about that\Nand get right to the Jinchuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the time to\Nbe joining you in your diversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides...at some point after\Nthis mission is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you to the next world\Nso that you won't get bored in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man... I hope our next opponent has enough\N fight in them so I can let off some steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei,\Nwhat're you going to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the cool thing...\NI wanted to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Rasengan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also use...\Nthe Rasengan, Kakashi Sensei?!
